messages.message:
Just FYI might be of interest but I also found an issues with & in names for annotation export; might be worth checking to see if that might be an issue too:

https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C02KS5FHZEE/p1688910795103459

that’s a separate issue with the code for exporting annotation sets in ML Studio

in general, it’s a common bug that we need to handle special characters in file paths

unfortunately, we currently don’t have one way to prevent all of these bugs in our platform

maybe worth considering adding logic to handle special characters to `ibfile` / `ibfile_v2`? @Heymian
